data.title: Billboard Explains: Record Labels
data.meta_description: Republic Records was Billboard's top record label of 2022. For a long time being signed to a label meant an artist made it into the music industry. But what does a record label actually do? What kind of power do they hold? How do they make a profit? How have they evolved with artists finding success online? This is Billboard Explains: Record Labels.
